    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm being gaslit by \"hope.\" every time someone tells me to \"take small actions,\" it feels like they're just trying to make me feel better about a doomed situation. i don't want to spend my whole life fighting a battle that's already lost. it's just so much more logical to just... stop fighting. to just opt out of this whole nightmare before it gets even worse. if the ship is definitely going down, why stay on board and struggle through the panic?",
